{"title":"访问阿尔巴尼亚首都","authors":["陈翰笙"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访问阿尔巴尼亚首都"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈翰笙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹰邦都城镇山谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山顶积雪皑夺目。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数公园绿满城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍植南国名花木。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国名出自珀虎斯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古时鹰将众所知。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨及希腊马基顿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"版图辽阔忆当时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯坎德培抗突厥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫古寨廿五载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立山腰如鹰巢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永示民族好光彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法西斯军苦蹂躏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗敌游击声威震。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战后重建社会新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三面顽敌不敢进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔予曾撰一专论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证实鹰国有祸根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英法德意谋瓜分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使节会议在伦敦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可喜三十六年后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躬自作客地拉那。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女欢娱握手多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊缤纷似花朵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白屋红顶处处新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机场广场了无尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月穿棕榈照来客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客在天涯若比邻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊皑［ái］、屹［yì］"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}